Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.64,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.64,0:00:20.18,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.80,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:53.55,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.55,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.36,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.50,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.50,0:01:22.85,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:27.58,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.58,0:01:34.52,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.74,0:02:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me... Could you repeat that, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I move that the Sorority be abolished!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.21,0:02:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-no-Kimi made a courageous speech,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...and took the assembly in a totally unexpected direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The student's frustration and resentment came to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a social caste system, for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it with those arrogant snobs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A problem like this is not one for discussion solely among ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't allow your emotions to get out of control!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's out of control?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're certain we can get the necessary two-thirds majority.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.66,0:02:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Go right ahead, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...if you think you can so easily abolish this venerated tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:03:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,30. The Petition
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,As you who attended the assembly heard already,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...I have spoken out against the existence of the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All students must be equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No one should decide who is better than whom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you agree with this statement,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...please sign this petition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, everyone had a lot they wanted to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...about what a problem the Sorority was.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't the school board hold it against me if I sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sorority is so close to the School Board,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm reluctant to risk signing my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The School Board consist of Sorority Alumni!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think a petition will have any effect on the School Board?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's it! That's why we have to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to stay at school that ignores petitions from the students?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to support the system that causes such a oppression?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this system even have the right to exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you are the one injured,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...or you are the one causing the injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...you both are victims of the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Our curriculum should teach us this:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...that all of us are free, and equal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm available to take your signature whenever you are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sign. I want to sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sign too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree with abolishing the Sorority too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, at lunchtime?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Beginning with today's lunchtime... we want everyone to see us,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...so, won't you please give us a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.76,0:05:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-no-Kimi would carry on all alone, but the more the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha... well, I'm not someone who likes attracting attention, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually kind of shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as the Sorority goes, I guess you could say I was against it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I don't really hate it enough to abolish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, I remember you saying just the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,... "This isn't all the fault of the Sorority".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole Sorority thing, it's so alien to me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really more your thing than mine, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:05:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who's sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.68,0:06:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't I ever do fashionable things like everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sign the petition!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sign to abolish the Sorority!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear brother... I'm surprised at myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it's not just me, there's Kaoru-no-Kimi too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.54,0:06:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She's shouting into a megaphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have thought this was totally unlike me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...even more so than Tomoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.03,0:06:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-no-Kimi, if I sign, would you autograph my notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Abolish the Sorority? She makes me so mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! Until recently she was a member.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How can that Misonoo-san girl change her position so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure seemed to enjoy the Sorority when she was a member.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, she's just that type. Anything goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't hear me say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But then again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, let's split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the assembly hall
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, then I'll take the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so strange... at first, my heart was pounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then bit by bit I felt more positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I even began looking forward to doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.42,0:07:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Nanako is actually rather good at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... sign your name there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't forget your grade and section.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push it! You made me scribble it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to look good, as long as it's legible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not nice, Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:07:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:07:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a petition to abolish the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sign our petition!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be careful whom you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You were a member, just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Until recently!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no class at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder that you were expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't expelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I resigned on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're shameless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakaya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you left on your own, unlike me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakaya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, should I put my name and section?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I could help too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really? Of course! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This crusade may be a good thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...but skipping lunch isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, Nanako! If I weren't looking after you all the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't misunderstand me. I'm no part of her crusade.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just here to be Nanako's manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What. What are you smiling at?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You! You, the nice lady there,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...just put your signature right here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...you mustn't put up with the Sorority!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you too, this way please, come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel quite right about doing it like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay! I have my own unique style at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I knew what Miya-sama was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... I did pretty well! I got five people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... I have eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I have six!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm a girl with a talent for getting signatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You do have a talent, Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the goal is a two-third majority?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. If we can get two-thirds of the students to sign,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...we can submit it directly to the school board.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's work and get 10 more after school!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. Let's do that, then visit Shinobu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,At her house?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Shinobu-san doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She's feeling much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But she can't stop worrying about Misaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.26,0:10:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She gets really depressed sometimes over what she did to Misaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're not going to stop for tea with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Not today, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki-san seems to be depressed since it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... She's not assertive and confident like she usually is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked her that way better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't feel right having tea, just us two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sonobe-san, Furuta-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.01,0:11:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Borgia-sama... Mona Lisa-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like to have a word with you, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how is Misaki-san's injury?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... she is getting much better...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But she doesn't really want to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Your coffee's getting cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you were aware that the Sorority has two vacancies now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...due to the departure of Shinobu-san and Misonoo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we have a vacancy,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...we can choose another candidate from the freshmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be quite a big occasion for the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many students who would want to be selected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...we thought about recommending Misaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama is very concerned about this petition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The thrust of this crusade is from your classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, if she were helpful to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:12:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...we could recommend her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Being in the Sorority was a dream of Misaki-san's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.29,0:13:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, since Junior High. Her more than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Each person has their own way of thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was floating along, aimless and giddy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...then something brought me back down to earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. They're in the locker room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened on the third day of the petition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the petition book.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ask Kaoru if you could burn it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I think not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Most certainly not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you disagree with me, say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't hide from discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But to do this, behind my back...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...it makes me sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you realize what you were doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something! Furuta-san! Sonobe-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let the Sorority be abolished!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:15:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's why I wanted to kill off this stupid campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of you too! You used to love the Sorority!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like to hear the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This was Misaki-san's idea, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The petition have been returned unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, let me finish, Kaoru-no-Kimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You two! Misaki-san put you up to doing this, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! It's just the thing Misaki-san would come up with!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Her accusation is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked Sonobe-san and Furuta-san to do this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,More than anyone, I wanted into the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,More than anyone, I admired the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I had committed my heart to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...something that a mere opportunist like you wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as you were abandoned by Miya-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...you ran off to join this petition campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll grab anything good that gets within reach,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...just like your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I resent that! How... how can you say such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're... you're nothing more than a wretched failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I am wretched.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone else says that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Misaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:16:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.96,0:17:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it because Mona-Lisa-sama and Borgia-sama asked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't ask us to do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it on our own!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do this, you'll get the blame for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.14,0:17:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't do me any more favors!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.32,0:17:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth! We weren't lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We did everything on our own!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They said if we could help the Sorority,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.72,0:17:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...she'd be recommended for membership.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.68,0:17:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Really! Misaki-san didn't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki-san wanted to protect us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She wanted to help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Believe us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, everything will be her fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We were worried about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She seemed so depressed recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why... that's why we had to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I hardly know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that enough? Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.99,0:18:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How long has it been...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...that I have been so detestable?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Aya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to take Halloween for walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Aya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is from the first year of junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, look at this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the fall tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.91,0:18:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The preliminary, to choose the anchor runner for the class relay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd already felt a sense of rivalry towards her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But at this point, the feeling became very strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what, I couldn't allow her to beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she must've felt the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She was first, I was second.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd passed the last turn, and were in the home straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why did you stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd have been the anchor if you hadn't stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It meant nothing if I won because you fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to beat you fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:19:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I absolutely hated her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I resolved never to let this girl even see me smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hate ran through my body like a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.49,0:20:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But now... it's very strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been through a lot since then, and now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now all that's left is an appreciation of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All I remember is that she was very straight, and very fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she has some good qualities. I admit that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Watching out for her friends, that's especially good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to apologize to Misaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.97,0:20:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Today... today I said something terrible to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay, Mariko, if I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.74,0:21:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.11,0:21:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She went out walking her dog, and isn't back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.48,0:21:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually she's back within half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.02,0:21:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she always goes to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you... do you love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.60,0:22:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, you'll be going home alone, Halloween.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.27,0:22:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.98,0:22:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.25,0:22:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.52,0:22:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This time... if it turns out you're the one who falls,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.13,0:22:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...then this time, I'll be the one who waits!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.29,0:22:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:22:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that, you'll not be the anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.16,0:23:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.25,0:23:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.31,0:23:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Previously unthinkable names appeared on the petition.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.40,0:23:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,From the freshmen, section B: Furuta Megumi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.91,0:23:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...as well as Sonobe Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.63,0:23:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, another...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.79,0:23:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki Aya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.23,0:23:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help us out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.62,0:23:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sign the petition to abolish the Sorority!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.16,0:24:14.36,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.36,0:24:19.83,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.30,0:24:25.44,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.44,0:24:30.91,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.65,0:24:37.19,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.19,0:24:42.66,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.66,0:24:45.39,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.39,0:24:48.20,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.20,0:24:50.60,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.60,0:24:55.87,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
